00:42:32.239 --> 00:42:37.600
here you probably want B to be on the second line as in the first line. So use column binding with

00:42:37.600 --> 00:42:42.639
caution. Make sure the data is arranged for you to do what you want to do. You can add the second

00:42:42.639 --> 00:42:48.959
